            <h4 class="text-success">üìå How to Calculate GPA</h4>
            <p>GPA (Grade Point Average) is calculated by dividing the total grade points earned by the total credit units taken in a semester.</p>
            <h5 class="text-primary">Formula:</h5>
            <p><b>GPA = Total Grade Points / Total Credit Units</b></p>
